OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCan India's Adani Group    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frecover from $100bn loss?  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, India's Adani Group has seen its market
OL,6, value plunge after a US investment firm
OL,7, made fraud allegations against it. Can 
OL,8, its ambitious growth plans survive?    
OL,10,FUntil two weeks ago, the               
OL,11,Fports-to-energy conglomerate which     
OL,12,Foperates seven publicly traded         
OL,13,Fcompanies had a combined valuation of  
OL,14,F$220bn.                                
OL,17,FThe Adani Group has denied the         
OL,18,Fallegations, calling them "malicious"  
OL,19,Fand "baseless" and says it plans have  
OL,20,Fnot changed. But investors are clearly 
OL,21,Fstill nervous.                         
